data.description: A wide front porch welcomes you into a beautiful townhome where the living room opens to the dining room. Step out to a generous screened porch overlooking a cheerful, private garden. Enjoy preparing meals in this renovated kitchen with its refurbished cabinets and new appliances. Upstairs, find two bedrooms, each with en suite bathroom. Ample storage throughout, two fireplaces, and front and back porches make this a special home. With recently-painted exterior and a 2-year-old roof, it’s also a carefree home. It’s an easy walk to downtown Tucker with its shops, restaurants, and weekly farmers market. This home is tucked back in a quiet community, but convenient to shopping, parks, festivals, Lawrenceville Highway, and I-285.
